# skip-rule: t-acc_obe
#: ../../user_manual/indi-remote-control.rst:44
#| msgid ""
#| "Since INDI is an independent backend component, you can run an INDI "
#| "server on a host without &kstars;. INDI can be compiled separately to run "
#| "on remote hosts. Furthermore, device drivers log messages to "
#| "<constant>stderr</constant> and that can be helpful in a debugging "
#| "situation. The syntax for INDI server is as following:"
msgid ""
"Since INDI is an independent backend component, you can run an INDI server "
"on a host without KStars. INDI can be compiled separately to run on remote "
"hosts. Furthermore, device drivers log messages to ``stderr`` and that can "
"be helpful in a debugging situation. The syntax for INDI server is as "
"following:"
msgstr ""
"Atès que INDI és un component de dorsal independent, podeu engegar un "
"servidor INDI en un client sense el KStars. INDI es pot compilar per "
"separat per a funcionar sobre les màquines remotes. A més, els controladors "
"de dispositius registren missatges a ``stderr`` (sortida d'error estàndard) "
"i això pot ser d'ajuda en una situació de depuració. La sintaxi del servidor "
"INDI és la següent:"

# skip-rule: t-acc_obe,t-sp_pu
#: ../../user_manual/indi-remote-control.rst:51
#| msgid ""
#| "$ <command>indiserver</command> [options] driver [<filename>driver</"
#| "filename> ...]"
msgid "$ **indiserver** [options] driver [``driver`` ...]"
msgstr "$ **indiserver** [opcions] driver [``controlador`` ...]"

# skip-rule: t-sp_2p,t-2p_sp
#: ../../user_manual/indi-remote-control.rst:53
#| msgid ""
#| "Options:\n"
#| " -l d     : Log driver messages to &lt;d&gt;/YYYY-MM-DD.islog\n"
#| " -m m     : Kill client if gets more than this many MB behind, default "
#| "128.\n"
#| " -d m     : Drop streaming blobs if client gets more than this many MB "
#| "behind, default 5. 0 to disable.\n"
#| " -p p     : Alternate IP port, default 7624.\n"
#| " -r r     : Maximum driver restarts on error, default 10.\n"
#| " -f path  : Path to fifo for dynamic startup and shutdown of drivers.\n"
#| " -v       : Show key events, no traffic.\n"
#| " -vv      : -v + key message content.\n"
#| " -vvv     : -vv + complete xml.\n"
#| " driver   : Executable or [device]@host[:port]"
msgid ""
"Options:\n"
" -l d     : Log driver messages to <d>/YYYY-MM-DD.islog\n"
" -m m     : Kill client if gets more than this many MB behind, default 128.\n"
" -d m     : Drop streaming blobs if client gets more than this many MB "
"behind, default 5. 0 to disable.\n"
" -p p     : Alternate IP port, default 7624.\n"
" -r r     : Maximum driver restarts on error, default 10.\n"
" -f path  : Path to fifo for dynamic startup and shutdown of drivers.\n"
" -v       : Show key events, no traffic.\n"
" -vv      : -v + key message content.\n"
" -vvv     : -vv + complete xml.\n"
" driver   : Executable or [device]@host[:port]"
msgstr ""
"Opcions:\n"
" -l d     : Registra els missatges del controlador a <d>/YYYY-MM-DD.islog.\n"
" -m m     : Tanca el client si genera més d'aquests MB, el valor "
"predeterminat és 10.\n"
" -d m     : Deixa anar els blobs de transmissió si el client obté més MB al "
"darrere, per a inhabilitar-ho de manera predeterminada és 5.0.\n"
" -p p     : Port IP alternatiu, el valor predeterminat és 7624.\n"
" -r r     : Màxim on el controlador reinicia l'error, el valor predeterminat "
"és 10.\n"
" -f path  : Camí al FIFO per a l'inici i tancament dinàmic dels "
"controladors.\n"
" -v       : Mostra els esdeveniments clau, menys trànsit.\n"
" -vv      : -v + el contingut del missatge clau.\n"
" -vvv     : -vv + &XML; complet.\n"
"controlador : Executable o [dispositiu]@amfitrió[:port]"

